    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that can only be described as a time capsule. This car is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since its original purchase. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from swirl marks, stone chips, or any imperfections, thanks to a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather seats remain firm and supple without a single crease, and the interior still carries that distinct factory-fresh scent. All technological features, including the advanced driver-assistance systems and premium audio, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by master technicians at authorized dealerships. It has never been driven in inclement weather and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this vehicle offers a rare opportunity to own a piece of automotive excellence in its purest form.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
